				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\theta$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M30"><mml:mi>θ</mml:mi></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="122_2019_3424_Article_IEq15.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> is the angle between rays in radians and <inline-formula id="IEq16"><alternatives><tex-math id="M31">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
