      <sec id="Sec9">
        <title>Spatial effect</title>
        <p id="Par28">We tested the independent row and column effects model, the separable first-order autoregressive (<inline-formula id="IEq61"><alternatives><tex-math id="M129">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
