      </sec>
      <sec id="Sec10">
        <title>Row and column effects model</title>
        <p id="Par29">Row and column effects can model the underlying smooth spatial field as well as external variation due to field management. We assumed:<disp-formula id="Equ10"><alternatives><tex-math id="M139">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
