				\begin{document}$${\varvec{\mu }}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M184"><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="bold-italic">μ</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="122_2019_3424_Article_IEq85.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> and the covariance matrix <inline-formula id="IEq86"><alternatives><tex-math id="M185">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
